id: setting/timezone-change
plugin: manual
_summary: Test to check if system timezone change is also done in the clock app
_description:
    PURPOSE:
        Test to check if system timezone change also updates the time in the clock app
    STEPS:
        1. Open the clock app.
        2. Click on the settings icon to open the settings page.
        3. Press the "Change time and date" setting.
        4. This should take you to the system-settings-app where you can change the timezone
        5. Once you change the timezone, return to the clock app
    VERIFICATION:
        Does the clock app show the correct time after the timezone change?
estimated_duration: 60
